Leonetti / O’Connell Family Foundation
















   



Menu





 
 



History








The Leonetti/O'Connell Family Foundation is a Delaware corporation formed on December 5th, 2005. It is the successor entity to the Caroline Leonetti Ahmanson Foundation, a California non-profit public benefit corporation formed on November 19, 1993. The foundation currently grants over 2 million dollars annually.
 
 
 



515 South Figueroa Street - Suite 1050 - Los Angeles, CA 90071
© Leonetti O'Connell Family Foundation 


















