At A Glance









                    The Leonetti/O'Connell Family Foundation                




                515 S. Figueroa St., Ste. 1050            

                Los Angeles,
                CA                United States                90071-3330                            

                                    Telephone: (213) 622-0066                            

                                    URL:
                    
                        www.locff.org


Type of Grantmaker

            Independent foundation        

Additional Descriptor





EIN

                203889415            
BRIDGE Number

                3822397610            










Background


Top of Page





                            Established in 1995 in CA as under The Caroline Leonetti Ahmanson Foundation. In 2004 its name was changed to The Leonetti/O’Connell Foundation.  It relocated and merged with its DE foundation in 2006.                        






Purpose and Activities


Top of Page




                    The focus of the foundation is education in Los Angeles County, CA.                




 


 
 


